title: The world's only love bank resides in central Slovakia
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Spectacular Slovakia sets out on a trip to Banská Štiavnica to relive an actual love story. Listen to how a bank, without money but filled with love boxes, preserves the old love story of Andrej Sládkovič and Marína Pišlová.   
 
Guest: Katarína Javorská  
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec
